larships    UIC Connection    Contact Us    UIC menu    UIC.edu    Campus Map       Search                        Student Resources     View Menu  Down arrow icon             Here To Serve  We are dedicated to creating an environment that allows students to achieve their full potential. The success and safety of UIC students is of utmost importance to Student Affairs and the larger campus community. The following information is provided for easy access to important policies, programs, and services.          Campus Dining & Meal Plans  Meeting the nutritional needs and the environmental expectations of University students, faculty, staff and visitors.          Career Services  Career Services empowers you to find your fit in the world of work.          Dean of Students  Offers services, programs and resources
    that contribute to student success          Financial Aid  The OSFA administers an array of federal, state and institutional programs          ID Center  Supports the university community with a standardized and convenient form of identification          Meetings & Events  Reserves space in Student Centers East and West for student organizations‚ faculty and staff and non-University groups          Orientation  Is an important step in your transition as a new student, and is designed to help you make the most of UIC.          Scholarships  Assists current UIC undergraduate and professional school students in searching and applying for scholarships.          Student Employment  Offers assistance to UIC students, departments and off-campus employers.          Student Legal Services  Is a full-service law office dedicated to providing legal solutions for currently enrolled students.          Student Assistance  Provides advocacy and support for
    students experiencing personal and academic challenges          Student Conduct  Encourages and supports responsible student behavior and
    oversees the Student Disciplinary Policy          Student Veteran Affairs  Provides caring and personalized support to UIC undergraduate and graduate student veterans.          UIC Bookstore          UIC Tech Center  is here to serve the technology purchase and repair needs of UIC Students, Faculty, Staff and Departments.              Resources    Back to main content           Campus Dining & Meal Plans    Career Services    Dean of Students    Financial Aid    ID Center    Meetings & Events    Orientation    Scholarships    Student Employment    Student Legal Services    Student Ombuds Services    Student Veterans Services    UIC Bookstores & Retail    UIC Tech Center                  UIC Logo        STUDENT AFFAIRS         For Employees    SA Portal    SA Human Resources    Leave Management    SA Technology      About Us    Mission & Vision    Strategic Priorities    Annual Report    Assessment    Giving Opportunities      INITIATIVES    U & I Care    UIC Connection    UIC Impact        BUTTON    Campus Safety    Contact Us    Support our Students         Contact   1200 West Harrison St., 3010 SSB  Chicago, IL 60607  Phone: (312) 996-7140  studentaffairs@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook    Twitter    Instagram    YouTube             UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  © 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings                 